  "identifier": "SB 251",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to the Department of Corrections.",
  "abstract": "Amend KRS 197.020 to establish that the Department of Corrections shall not be required to promulgate administrative regulations regarding the death penalty; establish that execution protocols and procedures may be prescribed by internal policy, memorandum, or another form of action; amend KRS 13A.105 to conform; make technical corrections.",
